These codes were originally written as part of the course materials of
the course "Computer Science 175: Computer Graphics", offered at Harvard
University by Steven J. Gortler.

The PRIMARY AUTHORS are (and/or have been):

    * Hamilton Chong
    * Guille D. Canas
    * Yuanchen Zhu
    * Steven J. Gortler

David Hunter later made modifications to this code for his CS 150 
class at Westmont College, Spring 2014.

